<p><i><b>The Age Of Spiritual Machines</b></i> is a book by <a href="/wiki/Futurology" title="Futurology">futurist</a> <a href="/wiki/Ray_Kurzweil" title="Ray Kurzweil" class="mw-redirect">Ray Kurzweil</a> about the future course of <a href="/wiki/Human_race" title="Human race" class="mw-redirect">humanity</a>, particularly relating to the development of <a href="/wiki/Artificial_intelligence" title="Artificial intelligence">artificial intelligence</a> and its impact on human <a href="/wiki/Consciousness" title="Consciousness">consciousness</a>. It is also a study on the concept of <a href="/wiki/Technological_singularity" title="Technological singularity">technological singularity</a>.</p>
